update.doc:
The <strong><code>update</code></strong> <a href="$MDN_URL$/Web/CSS">CSS</a> <a href="$MDN_URL$/Web/CSS/@media#media_features">media feature</a> can be used to test how frequently (if at all) the output device is able to modify the appearance of content once rendered.
<div>
```css
@media (update: < none | slow | fast >) {
  /* styles to apply if the update frequency of the output device is a match */
}
```
</div>

